605
00:38:04,232 --> 00:38:06,432
The real hero is the person

606
00:38:06,501 --> 00:38:08,167
who got killed
at the police station

607
00:38:08,236 --> 00:38:10,102
after you arrested him.

608
00:38:10,171 --> 00:38:12,738
