614
00:38:45,790 --> 00:38:47,540
He did.

615
00:38:47,575 --> 00:38:48,574
Caught the killer.

616
00:38:48,626 --> 00:38:49,909
Saved the kids.

617
00:38:49,994 --> 00:38:52,044
Saved everybody.

618
00:38:52,113 --> 00:38:53,629
